info: Get Information About The Bot Or Server

info.name: guildinfo
info.description: shows info about the current guild

info.name: help
info.description: List all of Dionysus's commands or a specific command

info.name: invite
info.description: Gives you a link to invite the bot

info.description: Gives you a link to the open source project of the bot

miscellaneous.name: apply
miscellaneous.description: Allows you to create an application

subcommands.name: list
subcommands.description: Allows you to view current application questions

subcommands.name: setup
subcommands.description: Allows you to set where clubs should be created and who is allowed to

subcommands.name: edit
subcommands.description: Allows you to edit a club
subcommands.example: club edit #art-&-drawing "Art & Design" "A place to design and draw art" https://example.com/link/to-image.jpg "Wednesdays 2:00 PM

subcommands.name: create
subcommands.description: Allows you to create a club
subcommands.example: club create #art-&-drawing "Art & Design" "A place to design and draw art" https://example.com/link/to-image.jpg "Wednesdays 2:00 PM

subcommands.name: delete
subcommands.description: Allows you to delete a club

subcommands.name: blacklist
subcommands.description: Allows you to blacklist someone from a club

miscellaneous.name: listmembers
miscellaneous.description: List servers members by a role or not

miscellaneous.name: ping
miscellaneous.description: Responds with the bots current ping between the client and discord

miscellaneous.name: roles
miscellaneous.description: Shows a list of all roles in the server

miscellaneous.name: say
miscellaneous.description: Sends a message as though it was sent by the bot

miscellaneous.name: settings
miscellaneous.description: Lets you view your configured bot settings or a specific one

miscellaneous.name: suggest
miscellaneous.description: Allows you to make a suggestion to the server

miscellaneous.name: update
miscellaneous.description: Allows you to update a members various stats

subcommands.name: rank
subcommands.description: Allows you to update someones rank for the leveling system

subcommands.name: messages
subcommands.description: Updates a members messages from a channel

subcommands.name: invites
subcommands.description: Updates a members invites

subcommands.name: partners

roles: Lets you do various things with roles

roles.name: autoposition
roles.description: Allows you to add roles based on someones join or creation date

subcommands.name: create
subcommands.description: Adds a role based on a accounts creation date

subcommands.name: join
subcommands.description: Adds a role based on a accounts join date

roles.name: autorole
roles.description: Sets what role will be given or removed automatically upon the user joining the guild
roles.detailedDescription: You can also optionally set a time for when this should occur

subcommands.name: add
subcommands.description: Adds a role upon the user joining the guild

subcommands.name: remove
subcommands.description: Removes a role upon the user joining the guild

roles.name: giverole
roles.description: Allows you to add or remove a role from a member; members, bots, or everyone

subcommands.name: add
subcommands.description: Adds a role to a member
subcommands.detailedDescription: You can optionally supply your member argument with everyone to execute for everyone in the guild, members to execute for all members, bots to execute for all bots, or an user

subcommands.name: remove
subcommands.description: Removes a role to a member
subcommands.detailedDescription: You can optionally supply your member argument with everyone to execute for everyone in the guild, members to execute for all members, bots to execute for all bots, or an user

roles.name: reactionrole
roles.description: Sets up a reaction role with a defined message and emoji

roles.name: role
roles.description: Allows you to create, edit or delete a role,

subcommands.name: create
subcommands.description: Creates a role with the specified name

subcommands.name: position
subcommands.description: Edits a roles current position

subcommands.name: color
subcommands.description: Edits a roles current color

subcommands.name: name
subcommands.description: Edits a roles name

subcommands.name: delete
subcommands.description: Deletes a role
